resultset.statement: select c.customer_id, c.first_name, c.last_name, c.email, a.address, a.address2, a.district, ci.city, co.country, postal_code, a.phone, c.active, c.create_date FROM customer c join address a on (c.address_id = a.address_id) JOIN city ci on (a.city_id = ci.city_id) JOIN country co on (ci.country_id = co.country_id) WHERE customer_id > 10
